433 Sense of Space - Mayakovsky CC0 Version
===========================================

This folder contains the Mayakovsky CC0 audio variant of 433 Sense of Space.

Embedded Ambience Audio
-----------------------

The ambience loop assets:

- `433_loop_10k_s8_stereo.bin`
- `433_loop_24k_s16_stereo.bin`
- the UF2 firmware images that embed those assets

are derived from:

- `Mayakovsky theatre main stage - spectators walking in, taking their seats, ambience OMNI mics.wav`
- Creator: `gladkiy`
- URL: https://freesound.org/people/gladkiy/sounds/347832/
- Licence: Creative Commons 0 / Public Domain Dedication

Seat Creak Audio
----------------

The seat creak asset:

- `seat_creak_12k_s8_stereo.bin`

is derived from:

- `Chair creaking back and forth 01.wav`
- Creator: `unkleceeg`
- URL: https://freesound.org/people/unkleceeg/sounds/276473/
- Licence: Creative Commons 0 / Public Domain Dedication

See `SEAT_CREAK_SOURCE.md` for the exact source notes and conversion details.

Firmware Source Code
--------------------

New project-specific source code in this folder may be used, modified, and shared
for any purpose.

Some source files are copied or adapted from existing Music Thing Modular Workshop
Computer / Pico SDK project material and retain their original notices and licence
status where applicable, including:

- `ComputerCard.h`
- `pico_sdk_import.cmake`
- `reverb_dsp.c`
- `reverb_dsp.h`

The embedded audio assets listed above are CC0 according to their Freesound source
pages.
